      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "みなさーん！　今日はありがとうございましたー！\n次回のライブも来てくれなきゃダメですよ～！",
      "startTime": 8.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3000,
          "startTime": 11.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "歓声が凄いな……いつもよりさらに熱量がある",
      "startTime": 12.5922448795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！　お疲れ様です～",
      "startTime": 19.7289117178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ、みんな凄かったよ\n特にこころは……本当に輝いてたな",
      "startTime": 26.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ……そうでしょうそうでしょう！\nこれがリズノワ次期センターの真の力です！",
      "startTime": 34.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "……とはいえ、まぁ、その～",
      "startTime": 38.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、{user}さんにも\nいろいろと相談に乗ってもらいましたし？",
      "startTime": 44.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "それなりに感謝してあげなくも……ないかな～",
      "startTime": 48.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "って、こら～！\n愛ちゃん、いつまで頭を撫でてるつもりですか～！",
      "startTime": 55.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "これじゃあぜんっぜん締まんないじゃないですか～！",
      "startTime": 59.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さて、残りの仕事を片付けるか\nあれ？　これは……チョコ？　一体誰が……",
      "startTime": 69.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6466.666666700007,
          "startTime": 75.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "あれれ～？\nとっても可愛いラッピングのチョコですね～？",
      "startTime": 78.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "どこの天使が置いてってくれたんでしょうね～？",
      "startTime": 82.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "こころ？　どうしたんだ？\n四人で打ち上げに行ったと思ってたんだが",
      "startTime": 89.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "行きましたよ～",
      "startTime": 92.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "「今日くらいはいいわよ」って莉央さんの\nお許しが出たので、沢山食べました～",
      "startTime": 96.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんの家で大盛りラーメンを食べてからの\n莉央さんオススメのパンケーキ……",
      "startTime": 103.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "デザートにしては多過ぎましたね……\nお腹一杯です～",
      "startTime": 109.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "それでまぁ、帰りにちょっとだけ\n事務所に寄ってみようかな～って思っただけですよ～",
      "startTime": 114.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "それよりも、そのチョコ、食べなくていいんですか～？\nきっと美味しいですよ～？",
      "startTime": 122.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、いただくかな。……うん、美味い！\nナッツの食感がいいアクセントになってるな",
      "startTime": 133.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "良かったです～\n愛ちゃんも美味しいって言ってました～",
      "startTime": 138.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "愛が？\nそれじゃあ、これはやっぱり……",
      "startTime": 142.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "こころは「愛ちゃんも美味しいって言ってた」\nとしか言ってないですよ～？",
      "startTime": 149.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ\n誰かは知らないが、美味しかった。ありがとう",
      "startTime": 153.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "は～い、誰が置いたのかは分かりませんけど\n感想とお礼はかわりに受け取りました～",
      "startTime": 161.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ私は帰りますね",
      "startTime": 164.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5166.6666667000245,
          "startTime": 169.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様で～す",
      "startTime": 167.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、今日のライブ、改めて……本当に良かった\n新曲も最高だったよ",
      "startTime": 178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 180.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "あ、一つ言い忘れてました\nそのチョコ、一個だけ違う味が混ざってるらしいです",
      "startTime": 186.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr024.m4a",
      "text": "と～っても苦いみたいですよ～",
      "startTime": 190.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　え！　なんでそんなことに……",
      "startTime": 193.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_03-kkr025.m4a",
      "text": "だって、甘いよりも苦い方が\n特別感が出るじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 200.7,
      "sfxList": []
